msgid "Scenario II: Return to The Last King"
msgstr "冒险II：重返最后的王者"

msgid "Remove Agenda 1a - \"Fashionably Late\" from the game and replace it with the new Agenda 1a - \"Better Never Than Late.\""
msgstr "将密谋la——“礼节性迟到”从游戏中移除，并用新的密谋la——“不到却比迟到好”替换。"

msgid "Set the Shocking Display treachery and the new Dianne Devine <i>(Hiding an Oath Unspoken)</i> ally aside, out of play. Remove the original Dianne Devine <i>(Mercurial and Mischevious)</i> from the game."
msgstr "将惊悚一幕诡计卡和新版的黛安娜·迪瓦恩<i>(隐藏禁忌誓约)</i>盟友放在一边，位于场外。将原版的黛安娜·迪瓦恩<i>(调皮捣蛋)</i>从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Place the 8 “Sickening Reality” story cards underneath the scenario reference card."
msgstr "将8张“令人作呕的现实”剧情卡放在冒险参考卡下方。"

msgid "In your Campaign Log, under “VIPs Slain,” record the name of each unique [[Possessed]] or [[Lunatic]] enemy in the victory display."
msgstr "在你的冒险日志的“贵宾遇害”下方记录胜利牌区中每个独特的[[附身]]或[[狂人]]敌人的名字。"
